Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H4B3E3D&\bord0\fs22\pos(504,245.8)\frz350.2}馬上到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H4B3E3D&\bord0\fs24\pos(488,417)\frz349}相馬 快來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他明明是怕狗的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H4B3E3D&\bord0\fs24\fad(50,0)\frz348.2\pos(460.8,623.4)}話說夏目家養狗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:21:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼叫話說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs28\c&H332827&\pos(1022,452.2)}我想習慣一下 能陪我特訓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,明明不知道人家的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@FZShaoEr-M11\fs28\bord0\c&H29262B&\frz246.1\pos(944,346.6)}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.47,0:22:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我在幹什麼呢
